Subject: a11y iOS: Provide translations for the new Rotor names for TextEdit

VoiceOver has the Rotor that allows it to change the text navigation on
editable components between character, word, line, sentence etc..
We already extended the iOS a11y bridge and provide the translations
for the user facing-strings here.

[ChangeLog][Accessibility][iOS] Provide translations for the new
custom Rotor names for TextEdit

Fixes: QTBUG-139943
Change-Id: Idba7c540939638f34bda5115bc273008aa98afad
